--------------------------------------------------
About Leapfrog
--------------------------------------------------

This is the LeapFrog Jabber Client Project for SAPO.

How to build a release:
    $ cd lilypad
    $ xcodebuild -configuration Release -target Leapfrog
	(The resulting application bundle will be in ../SAPO_Messenger)


